'''sundo''' is a [[Quenya]] name meaning "base, root, root-word"<ref>{{LR|Etymologies}}, entry SUD (note that the root was changed to [[STUD]])</ref> and refers to an [[Elvish]] consonantal "base".
==Etymology==
From [[PQ]] *''thund≈ç'', [[root]] [[STUD]]<ref>{{VT|46a}} p.16</ref>
